data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Johnstown! This spacious end-unit townhome offers the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, and modern living. With 2 primary suites, a total of 3 bedrooms, 3 and 1/2 bathrooms, and a host of desirable features, this property won't last long.Key Features:2 Primary Suites: Enjoy the ultimate in comfort and privacy with not one, but two primary suites. Each suite offers a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom, making it perfect for families or guests. Open Concept Living: Step inside to an open and inviting living space with vaulted ceilings that create a sense of grandeur. And you'll love the gas fireplace in the living room on chilly evenings.Spacious Kitchen: The kitchen features a center island with plenty of seating, quartz countertops, and ample storage space. It's perfect for preparing meals and entertaining friends and family. Don't miss the large corner pantry.Partially Finished Basement: The mostly unfinished basement offers endless possibilities for customization and expansion. With one bedroom and one bathroom already in place, you can use the rest of space for a home office, a gym, a recreation room, or whatever suits your lifestyle.Scenic Patio: This townhome backs to a tranquil green space, providing a serene and private outdoor retreat. Enjoy your morning coffee on the patio or host summer barbecues with friends in this peaceful setting.Location: Nestled in the desirable Rolling Hills Ranch subdivision, this townhome is conveniently located near all the new development that is happening in Johnstown. There's a shopping center and a Buc-ee's opening soon just 3 miles away. Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or exploring the local attractions, everything is just minutes away. Experience the best of Johnstown living with luxury, space, and convenience. Schedule a showing today and start envisioning your future in this remarkable home!
